${project.name}

  The ${project.name} is a skin for Maven generated sites. It is derived from the {{{http://andreasviklund.com/templates/1024px}1024px}} template by {{{http://andreasviklund.com}Andreas Viklund}}.

  The site you are currently seeing is generated using this skin.

* Usage

  To use ${project.artifactId} as your Maven generated site skin, declare it in the <<<site.xml>>> descriptor:

+-----
<project>
  ...
  <skin>
    <groupId>${project.groupId}</groupId>
    <artifactId>${project.artifactId}</artifactId>
    <version>${project.version}</version>
  </skin>
  ...
</project>
+-----
